comment: /**  * Returns the serialized form of the original exception.  */
code: /**  * Returns the serialized form of the original exception.  */ public SerializedThrowable getException() {     return exception. }

comment: /**  * Returns the contained exception as a string.  *  * @return failure causing exception as a string, or {@code "(null)"}  */
code: /**  * Returns the contained exception as a string.  *  * @return failure causing exception as a string, or {@code "(null)"}  */ public String getExceptionAsString() {     return exception.getFullStringifiedStackTrace(). }

comment: /**  * Returns the timestamp for the contained exception.  *  * @return timestamp of contained exception, or 0 if no exception was set  */
code: /**  * Returns the timestamp for the contained exception.  *  * @return timestamp of contained exception, or 0 if no exception was set  */ public long getTimestamp() {     return timestamp. }
